WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
笙ｪAllergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive笙ｪ

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
笙ｪJust like a hug needs
the right body heat笙ｪ

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
笙ｪYour "same here" carries
a touch of resolve笙ｪ

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
笙ｪPack my bags, we can set off right now笙ｪ

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
笙ｪThe future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure笙ｪ

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
笙ｪThe journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination笙ｪ

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
笙ｪThose moments together
are what bind us strongest笙ｪ

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
笙ｪConnect笙ｪ

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
笙ｪLet's go!笙ｪ

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
笙ｪLeave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality笙ｪ

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
笙ｪToday, no dwelling
on negative emotions笙ｪ

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
笙ｪTomorrow holds more luck笙ｪ

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
笙ｪTogether we'll create moving melodies笙ｪ

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
笙ｪThe future begins to take shape笙ｪ

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.225
=Episode 13=

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.100
Mom.

00:01:10.062 --> 00:01:12.162
(Grave of Mother, Shen Qi)

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.360
I've been wondering...

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:17.637
What exactly did you give me?

00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:23.320
From my earliest memories,

00:01:25.240 --> 00:01:26.600
it was always Grandma's face.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.412
I always felt like
she was a bit impatient.

00:01:31.062 --> 00:01:32.437
(Loving Mother)

00:01:32.437 --> 00:01:34.660
She was impatient
when she took me out to get some sun.

00:01:36.450 --> 00:01:38.810
She was impatient
when she told me stories, too.

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:42.840
It wasn't until
my sister came to find me

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:46.000
that I realized

00:01:47.737 --> 00:01:49.450
love is actually like this.

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:56.400
It's telling
fun stories together in bed.

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.400
It's wearing pretty clothes together.

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:03.320
It's holding my hand

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.640
and teaching me how to draw.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.320
Mom,

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:18.400
(Loving Mother)
sister has passed away from illness.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:22.840
Now, it seems like I'm sick too.

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:26.000
Why me?

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:31.240
I never even had a decent childhood.

00:02:38.175 --> 00:02:39.187
You know what?

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:44.080
I met

00:02:45.625 --> 00:02:47.665
a very wonderful person.

00:02:49.075 --> 00:02:51.555
I haven't even had
the chance to love him properly yet.

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:56.800
I don't want to go.

00:03:09.437 --> 00:03:11.025
(Grave of Loving Mother, Shen Qi)

00:03:11.025 --> 00:03:13.387
(Hai City People's Hospital)

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:28.240
I will definitely
take good care of myself.

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.040
Miss Lu,

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:35.760
this place...

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:37.560
was rented by a painter.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.560
I heard he went abroad later,

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:41.120
so it's been vacant.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.480
If you want to rent it,

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.760
the price is quite reasonable.

00:03:44.760 --> 00:03:45.680
I'll take it.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:48.360
Wonderful. Miss Lu,
you really have an eye for this.

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:49.640
The rent is...

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:50.600
I'm buying it.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.680
Buying it?

00:03:55.375 --> 00:03:58.135
I want a place
that belongs entirely to me.

00:03:58.737 --> 00:04:00.017
It can't be a rental.

00:04:01.050 --> 00:04:02.470
Please help me figure something out.

00:04:03.212 --> 00:04:05.372
Yes, of course.
I'll call the owner right now.

00:04:05.450 --> 00:04:06.890
Please wait a moment.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.840
(Sister once told me)

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:50.120
(that throughout her short life,)

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:52.440
(she was always
playing different roles.)

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:55.000
(A daughter,)

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.520
(the Miss Lu of the Lu family,)

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.800
(and my sister.)

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:03.240
(When she was immersed
in each of those identities,)

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:05.680
(she would lose herself
for long periods of time.)

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:09.480
(To the point where,
other than her name,)

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:13.480
(everything else about Lu Zhu
was bestowed upon her by others.)

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.080
(But I am different.)

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:17.880
(I am Sun,)

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:21.640
(as in a little bamboo shoot breaking
through the soil after the rain.)

00:05:22.560 --> 00:05:23.960
(I want to be myself.)

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.360
(I need to hurry)

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:29.000
(and be my true self.)

00:05:58.440 --> 00:05:59.720
Why are you so happy today?

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:07.280
My studio.

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:14.120
I've been thinking about what to do
with the summer of my 19th year.

00:06:14.220 --> 00:06:15.520
Recently, I came up with an idea.

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:18.680
I can hold an art exhibition
on the day of the summer solstice.

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:22.200
That sounds like a great idea.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:23.160
So,

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:25.600
will you go?

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.680
That depends on your performance.

00:06:31.080 --> 00:06:32.720
What do you mean, "my performance?"

00:06:33.480 --> 00:06:36.225
Are you going or not?

00:06:36.250 --> 00:06:37.650
笙ｪYou always tell me to get up early笙ｪ

00:06:37.700 --> 00:06:41.113
笙ｪSo why didn't you stop at night?笙ｪ

00:06:41.500 --> 00:06:46.060
笙ｪThe clock goes tick-tock, tick-tock笙ｪ

00:06:47.940 --> 00:06:52.060
笙ｪThe clock goes tick-tock, tick-tock笙ｪ

00:06:53.100 --> 00:06:58.980
笙ｪI want to whisper
"I love you" into your ear笙ｪ

00:06:58.980 --> 00:07:05.380
笙ｪI want to hold you tight
because I miss you笙ｪ

00:07:05.380 --> 00:07:08.260
笙ｪOur relationship is like a play笙ｪ

00:07:08.260 --> 00:07:11.580
笙ｪOur love needs no words笙ｪ

00:07:11.580 --> 00:07:16.980
笙ｪI just want to be close,
just want to be close to you笙ｪ

00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:20.660
笙ｪWe could have a couple of kids笙ｪ

00:07:20.660 --> 00:07:23.580
笙ｪWe could live
in a house in the country笙ｪ

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:26.620
笙ｪHave time to talk about
what's on our minds笙ｪ

00:07:26.620 --> 00:07:29.900
笙ｪAll the love
revolves around loving you笙ｪ

00:07:29.900 --> 00:07:33.540
笙ｪThe summer breeze blows past my ear笙ｪ

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:44.000
- Some soup?
- I can't.

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:45.640
I'm nauseous.

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:47.000
Is it that bad?

00:07:47.860 --> 00:07:48.880
I'll get you some water.

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:49.560
Okay.

00:07:51.320 --> 00:07:53.200
It was the same
when I was pregnant with Man.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.880
It lasted for several months.

00:07:59.080 --> 00:08:00.200
Mom, have some water.

00:08:07.880 --> 00:08:09.320
Mom and Mr. Lu,

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:10.280
I'm full.

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:12.290
I still have data to work on,
so I'll head up first.

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:12.960
Okay.

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:17.960
Hey, Lu.

00:08:18.300 --> 00:08:19.100
Wait a second.

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:20.680
I have something to tell you.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:23.960
What is it?

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:25.320
In a few days,

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:27.240
I'm inviting the recruitment teachers

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:29.360
from a national school
in Singapore for dinner.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:31.000
You should come along then.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:33.360
You're sending me to study abroad?

00:08:33.975 --> 00:08:36.135
What else are you going to do
at your age if not study?

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:40.560
But didn't you want me to be an intern

00:08:41.010 --> 00:08:42.600
and help you with background screening?

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:46.720
Your brother's project

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:48.920
will be finished next month.

00:08:48.920 --> 00:08:50.920
Once it's done,
you'll go for further studies.

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.440
Study hard.

00:08:52.675 --> 00:08:53.795
When you return,

00:08:53.795 --> 00:08:56.512
you can help share the family's burden.

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:00.512
I understand.

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:25.800
Be honest.

00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:27.920
What's the deal with the Lily Fan?

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:29.840
Are you jealous?

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:33.320
I saw her kiss you last time.

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:35.480
If she's just a regular colleague,

00:09:35.875 --> 00:09:37.955
there's no need to greet you like that.

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:42.800
She's my ex-girlfriend.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.520
But we broke up a long time ago.

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:49.560
And then?

00:09:49.560 --> 00:09:51.600
And now she's my business partner.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.190
She came back
to help me with my startup.

00:09:55.160 --> 00:09:57.000
I think she still has feelings for you.

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:01.000
After all,
you two see each other all the time.

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:09.960
I can hear it now.

00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:14.720
You really are jealous.

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.600
Well, there is a precedent.

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:21.840
For people like us
who see each other all the time,

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:24.360
it's very easy
to end up in bed together.

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:31.920
Have you ever thought

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.240
what would happen if they found out?

00:10:37.280 --> 00:10:38.600
If they found out,

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:41.760
they would definitely
do everything they could to stop us.

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:45.280
So we have to make use
of every moment we have

00:10:46.600 --> 00:10:48.320
before that day comes.

00:10:49.220 --> 00:10:50.480
We can't waste a single second.

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:10.280
Go ahead.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:21.440
Goodnight, Mr. Ye.

00:11:38.487 --> 00:11:42.987
笙ｪBit by bit, I'll forget you笙ｪ

00:11:43.212 --> 00:11:47.000
笙ｪBit by bit, I'll erase the memories笙ｪ

00:11:47.175 --> 00:11:51.250
笙ｪFrom now on,
your image won't linger in my mind笙ｪ

00:11:51.250 --> 00:11:55.387
笙ｪNor will those fragments of the past笙ｪ

00:11:55.512 --> 00:11:59.287
笙ｪDays will slowly drift away
like passing clouds笙ｪ

00:11:59.287 --> 00:12:03.062
笙ｪI'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone笙ｪ

00:12:03.062 --> 00:12:05.337
笙ｪThe you in my memories笙ｪ

00:12:05.337 --> 00:12:07.350
笙ｪWill fade from clarity笙ｪ

00:12:07.350 --> 00:12:12.787
笙ｪHow much longer must I wait to笙ｪ

00:12:14.350 --> 00:12:19.787
笙ｪForget you completely笙ｪ